{"data":{"allAboutMarkdown":{"sections":[{"frontmatter":{"imageAlt":"About Cheuk Kit","imageSrc":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/67be4432e73fefea12d8442dc8468d05/58b3a/DSC_2570.jpg","srcSet":"/static/67be4432e73fefea12d8442dc8468d05/a77c0/DSC_2570.jpg 100w,\n/static/67be4432e73fefea12d8442dc8468d05/ac9f5/DSC_2570.jpg 200w,\n/static/67be4432e73fefea12d8442dc8468d05/58b3a/DSC_2570.jpg 400w,\n/static/67be4432e73fefea12d8442dc8468d05/91225/DSC_2570.jpg 800w","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/67be4432e73fefea12d8442dc8468d05/64a37/DSC_2570.webp 100w,\n/static/67be4432e73fefea12d8442dc8468d05/cb817/DSC_2570.webp 200w,\n/static/67be4432e73fefea12d8442dc8468d05/d603c/DSC_2570.webp 400w,\n/static/67be4432e73fefea12d8442dc8468d05/1a949/DSC_2570.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"}]},"width":400,"height":267}}}},"html":"<p>My name is Cheuk Kit. I am a software developer with 3 years of industrial experiences.</p>\n<p>Being more specialised in backend software development, however, I am also experienced in frontend web development, as well as Ethereum Smart Contracts (ERC20, ERC721).</p>\n<p>I also see myself as a hybrid person. Not only am I equipped with software engineering skills, I am also highly eager to explore beyond the coding environment, such as running for Discord NFT moderators in some projects.</p>"}]}}}